{"tid":2138589,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【蘋果踢爆】警福利基金秘改採購程序 副處長審批金額增兩倍","createTime":"2020-08-03T16:26:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-03T17:47:59.000Z","uid":240362,"like":9,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"d52c918fa57ae291228eb1e2915cf43e921bcf21","tid":2138589,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:26:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/CM73W63KCBDDVNUDUVTEGIVQJQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FCM73W63KCBDDVNUDUVTEGIVQJQ%2F&d=vyHMe5JNZh87BdTcd5o0O%2FcbRDcn212Q0H9cnoVtDxk%3D&h=7284fd51\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200804%2FCM73W63KCBDDVNUDUVTEGIVQJQ%2F&h=4bbf8397\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200804/CM73W63KCBDDVNUDUVTEGIVQJQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭政府治下，警權無限擴大。《蘋果》發現，警隊去年底透過修改《警察通例》，放寬警察福利基金的採購程序。過往基金若涉超過50萬元的購物或服務費開支，會進行招標遴選程序，並由基金投標委員會考慮及批核；惟警方去年底放寬限制，開支金額要達到140萬元以上，才需經委員會批核；金額介乎50萬至140萬元的開支，僅交由警務處副處長（管理）批核即可。立法會議員林卓廷批評有關改動是監察上的倒退。"},{"pid":"a291eae71bed16eafe4a406e43cfe25985309267","tid":2138589,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"411152c6a2eb575f7fd2f0693c915aa9e9fe6a6f","tid":2138589,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"夾埋一齊推<br />\n<br />\n【蘋果踢爆】警福利基金「無名氏」千萬不明捐款 保安局指引：應識別捐款人<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2138575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2138575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a4afe91ba1ebdc35fc0f5e20b21c5679d25691e9","tid":2138589,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a291eae71bed16eafe4a406e43cfe25985309267","tid":2138589,"uid":284432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:29:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-03T16:34:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/f